          {
            "xhtmlFragment": "...A covenant not to <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">sue</span> sets out the patent <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">owner&apos;s</span> agreement not to <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">sue</span> the alleged infringer for patent infringement concerning the specific patent identified. It may also be limited to certain specific products or processes of the alleged infringer, and the patent <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">owner&apos;s</span> counsel may vary the sample covenant&apos;s scope based on the specific product definition used. The patent <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">owner&apos;s</span> counsel may also consider whether to limit the covenant to a specific field or territory....",
            "snippetLink": "/Document/Ibabdd72c642411e38578f7ccc38dcbee/View/FullText.html?navigationPath=Search%2Fv1%2Fresults%2Fnavigation%2Fi0accc0be0000018db3c3198fa64a92f0%3Fppcid%3Di0accc0c30000018db3c36215aa1fca50%26Nav%3DKNOWHOW%26fragmentIdentifier%3DIbabdd72c642411e38578f7ccc38dcbee%26parentRank%3D0%26startIndex%3D0%26transitionType%3DSearchItem&listSource=Search&list=KNOWHOW&rank=1&ppcid=i0accc0c30000018db3c36215aa1fca50&originationContext=Search%20Result&transitionType=SearchItem&isSnapSnippetLink=true#co_snip_24776"
          },
          {
            "xhtmlFragment": "...The alleged infringer should also consider whether the patent <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">owner</span> has any relevant pending patent applications at the time the patent <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">owner</span> provides the covenant. Although courts may not extend a covenant not to <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">sue</span> to a patent that was still a pending patent application at the time of the covenant, a court may instead, depending on the circumstances, determine that the patent <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">owner</span> licensed the patent resulting from the patent application to the alleged infringer (see 3M Innovative Properties Co. v. Barton Nelson, Inc., 2003 WL 22989077, at *2 (D. Minn. 2003))....",
            "snippetLink": "/Document/Ibabdd72c642411e38578f7ccc38dcbee/View/FullText.html?navigationPath=Search%2Fv1%2Fresults%2Fnavigation%2Fi0accc0be0000018db3c3198fa64a92f0%3Fppcid%3Di0accc0c30000018db3c36215aa1fca50%26Nav%3DKNOWHOW%26fragmentIdentifier%3DIbabdd72c642411e38578f7ccc38dcbee%26parentRank%3D0%26startIndex%3D0%26transitionType%3DSearchItem&listSource=Search&list=KNOWHOW&rank=1&ppcid=i0accc0c30000018db3c36215aa1fca50&originationContext=Search%20Result&transitionType=SearchItem&isSnapSnippetLink=true#co_snip_18847"
