        "snippets": [
          {
            "xhtmlFragment": "...I found myself in a <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">bit</span> of a quandary. I did not feel that I could achieve my career goals by working three days a week, even though that is exactly what I had asked for. And I could not be present for my family as much as I wanted to be working five days a week. I realized that I needed to take a step back and think outside the box about what to do next. And once I stepped away, I realized pretty quickly that I wanted to do something to help people solve this work-parenting dilemma....",
            "snippetLink": "/Document/I62f25edc34a211ed9f24ec7b211d8087/View/FullText.html?navigationPath=Search%2Fv1%2Fresults%2Fnavigation%2Fi0accc0be0000018db3c3198fa64a92f0%3Fppcid%3Di0acc3c870000018db3c3621403786876%26Nav%3DKNOWHOW%26fragmentIdentifier%3DI62f25edc34a211ed9f24ec7b211d8087%26parentRank%3D0%26startIndex%3D0%26transitionType%3DSearchItem&listSource=Search&list=KNOWHOW&rank=3&ppcid=i0acc3c870000018db3c3621403786876&originationContext=Search%20Result&transitionType=SearchItem&isSnapSnippetLink=true#co_snip_11199"
          },
          {
            "xhtmlFragment": "...Zoe Sinclair is the Co-Founder of This Can Happen, which supports employers and employees to create a positive environment for good mental health in the workplace. She is also the <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">Owner</span> of Employees Matter, which is dedicated to delivering information from experts to assist employees in better managing the demands of both their personal and professional lives. Both This Can Happen and Employees Matter originated in the UK but have gradually expanded to support workplaces in the US and other countries around the world. This Can Happen is holding its first US online conference November 7-10, 2022 (see Box: This Can Happen)....",
            "snippetLink": "/Document/I62f25edc34a211ed9f24ec7b211d8087/View/FullText.html?navigationPath=Search%2Fv1%2Fresults%2Fnavigation%2Fi0accc0be0000018db3c3198fa64a92f0%3Fppcid%3Di0acc3c870000018db3c3621403786876%26Nav%3DKNOWHOW%26fragmentIdentifier%3DI62f25edc34a211ed9f24ec7b211d8087%26parentRank%3D0%26startIndex%3D0%26transitionType%3DSearchItem&listSource=Search&list=KNOWHOW&rank=3&ppcid=i0acc3c870000018db3c3621403786876&originationContext=Search%20Result&transitionType=SearchItem&isSnapSnippetLink=true#co_snip_5062"
          },
          {
            "xhtmlFragment": "...A Q&amp;A with Zoe Sinclair, Co-Founder of This Can Happen and <span class=\"co_searchTerm\">Owner</span> of Employees Matter. Practical Law Senior Legal Editor Jessica Cherry spoke with Zoe about her career pivot from BBC television producer to innovator and leader in workplace mental health. Zoe addresses how workplaces are evolving to better support the mental health of their employees, and the importance of breaking down silos and communicating with one another across industries, sectors, and geographies to improve workplace mental health and well-being. Zoe also identifies what she believes are the most significant barriers to better mental health and well-being in the legal industry and suggests strategies for overcoming these barriers....",
            "snippetLink": "/Document/I62f25edc34a211ed9f24ec7b211d8087/View/FullText.html?navigationPath=Search%2Fv1%2Fresults%2Fnavigation%2Fi0accc0be0000018db3c3198fa64a92f0%3Fppcid%3Di0acc3c870000018db3c3621403786876%26Nav%3DKNOWHOW%26fragmentIdentifier%3DI62f25edc34a211ed9f24ec7b211d8087%26parentRank%3D0%26startIndex%3D0%26transitionType%3DSearchItem&listSource=Search&list=KNOWHOW&rank=3&ppcid=i0acc3c870000018db3c3621403786876&originationContext=Search%20Result&transitionType=SearchItem&isSnapSnippetLink=true#co_snip_975"
          },
